title: [Yegharren Valley, Forest]
description: A sprawling thicket of blackberry bushes threatens to overrun the path here, its tangled branches forming ominous shapes in the filtered moonlight.  The roots of the surrounding oaks crisscross the open ground, peeking out from the thick carpet of dirt and leaves.

A sprawling thicket of blackberry bushes threatens to overrun the path here, its tangled branches populated by a small flock of multicolored forest birds that whistle noisily as they feed on the ripe berries.  The roots of the surrounding oaks crisscross the open ground, peeking out from the thick carpet of dirt and leaves.
